attributes.title: PANIC AT THE PIER • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.caption: HE'S TOUCHING ME INAPPROPRIATELY!!!
attributes.description: In beautiful Southern California, even the winters are warm enough for a nice trip to the beach.  And that seems like the perfect place to find some Pokemon.  Luckily, everyone at the pier was super helpful and friendly and wanted nothing but to help James, Aleks, and Alec catch some of their favorite Pokemon.
attributes.display_title: PANIC AT THE PIER • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE

attributes.title: DEATH BRINGS THE PAIN • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.caption: HE HIT ME IN THE NUTS SOO HARD!!
attributes.description: After meeting their social requirement of being outside for an hour, the boys retreat back to the safety of the warehouse for more Pokemon action.  But when death comes knocking at the door, they realize that they were actually safer outside.
attributes.display_title: DEATH BRINGS THE PAIN • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE

attributes.title: RUBBIN THE SEAMAN • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.caption: YOU GOT HIM KILLED!!!
attributes.description: Aleks' balls have finally seemed to recover just in time to play with more seamen.  All aboard on yet another battle filled episode on the S.S. Get Your Pokemon Killed Here.  Who knows what will happen.

attributes.caption: I THINK I HAD STROKE!!
attributes.description: This is it.  The final battle.  We only have a handful of Pokemon left, and are about to battle a gym that will surely kill us and finally put an end of this series.  One can only hope.

attributes.caption: WHY IS SHE WALKING LIKE THAT?!?
attributes.description: GAMEPLAY!!!  Holy crap we're playing a PC game!  I haven't seen those computers in years!!!  But after playing a game like Pacify, the nightmare fueled comedy starring Aleks and Alec, we might never see those computers again.  Oh well, best of luck fellas!
attributes.display_title: THE PACIFY NIGHTMARE

attributes.title: GETTING ADDICTED TO JAPANESE UFO CATCHERS
attributes.caption: THIS GAME IS RIGGED?!?
attributes.description: Who loves playing online games?!?  Club Penguin am I right?!?  Well too bad!!!  We're traveling all the way to Japan, via the internet, to blow more of our valuable money on worthless prizes and rigged crane games that are probably sitting in someones garage.  What will the great land of Japan bestow upon us for our mighty crane efforts???
attributes.display_title: GETTING ADDICTED TO JAPANESE UFO CATCHERS

attributes.title: THE BLOOD BATH OF MORDHAU
attributes.caption: HE HAS A HORSE!!!

Of course since we brought these puppies out we had to play the most popular game out there, Mordhau!!!!  Why?  Because horses!!!

attributes.title: THE BLOOD BATH OF MORDHAU - Part 2

attributes.title: WE'RE HORRIBLE HUNTERS
